Title: FOR GOD SO LOVED THE WORLD (因为神爱世人)
CCLI: 757

Verse 1 English:
For
He gave His only Son
To die on Calv’ry’s tree
From sin to set me free;
Some day He’s coming back —
What glory that will be!
Wonderful His love to me!

Verse 2 English:
(No English translation)

Verse 1 Chinese:
约 3:16

Verse 1 Chinese:
因为神爱世人，
舍了独生爱子，
钉死在十架上，
使我脱罪权势。
有日，祂要再来，
何等尊贵、荣耀！
祂的大爱真奇妙！

Verse 2 Chinese:
神非常爱世人，甚至将祂爱子，
也赐给了他们，叫一切信祂的，
不仅不至灭亡，反得永远生命。
神的大爱真奇妙！
